Stack:
ruby 1.9.1p378
Rubygems 1.3.5
Rails 3.0.0.beta
Haml
Datamapper 0.10.2
Mysql 5.X

Configure a local development instance:
Create a database called ambernet_development and grant a user access to it
Using config/database.yml.sample as an example, create your own config/database.yml

Install Gems:
bundle install

Populate Database:
unzip db/ambernet.zip (password protected)
rake db:populate 

Start the Application:
script/rails server

NOTE - rails3_datamapper is currently broken it seems and the application does not start up